{
  "texts": [
    "As illustrated in Fig. 3B, three studies validate their proposals by using the Hyperledger Caliper test platform, two by using statistical methods, and the other seven studies by using IoT-Lab, machine learning algorithms, CP-SNARK, the System Usability Scale (SUS) Survey, the Goerli Test Network, Questionnaires, and Smart Contracts to test or validate their study data or system.",
    "In the remaining studies, however, no validation method is mentioned.",
    "RQ3.2 Can the study data and methodologies be reused or repeated?This RQ has investigated the reusability and repeatability of the studies.",
    "Accordingly, only seven studies have addressed this aspect.",
    "One study shared a GitHub repository for reusability."
  ]
}